12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 321, O.S.L.
14 2024 (63 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 427.29), is amended to read as
15 follows:
16 Section 427.29. A. There is hereby created the Oklahoma
17 Medical Marijuana Authority Executive Advisory Council.
18 B. The Oklahoma Medical Marijuana Authority Executive Advisory
19 Council shall consist of the following members, and all appointees
20 shall serve their terms at the pleasure of the appointing authority
21 and may be removed or replaced without cause:
22 1. One member appointed by the Governor to represent all
23 citizens of this state;
24
