1 Nove mber 1, 2025, and no later than November 1 of each year
2 thereafter.
3 J. K. Members appointed pursuant to subsection B of this
4 section shall serve without compensation but shall be reimbursed for
5 expenses incurred in the performance of their duties in accordance
6 with the State Travel Reimbursement Act.
7 K. L. The Oklahoma Medical Marijuana Authority Executive
8 Advisory Council shall meet as often as necessary to conduct
9 business but shall meet not less than four times a year, with an
10 organizational meeting to be held prior to January 1, 2025.
11 L. M. Any vacancy occurring on the Oklahoma Medical Marijuana
12 Authority Executive Advisory Council shall be filled for the
13 unexpired term of office in the same manner as provided for in
14 subsection B of this section.
15 M. N. The Advisory Council shall act in accordance with the
16 provisions of the Oklahoma Open Meeting Act, the Oklahoma Open
17 Records Act, and the Administrative Procedures Act.
18 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
